These are three major
features of the tool.

00:10:46.936 --> 00:10:48.646 A:middle
And this is what I'll
be spending the rest

00:10:48.646 --> 00:10:51.406 A:middle
of the session telling you
more details and give you demos

00:10:51.406 --> 00:10:52.606 A:middle
of these three features.

00:10:53.256 --> 00:10:54.726 A:middle
So what are these
three features?

00:10:55.646 --> 00:10:57.266 A:middle
First, we have Inspection.

