So, suppose we have
a button here

00:20:44.876 --> 00:20:45.916 A:middle
that has eight dots in there.

00:20:46.776 --> 00:20:52.866 A:middle
In the Inspection tab on the top
section there's the Quick Look.

00:20:52.866 --> 00:20:58.846 A:middle
And on the left side we have
the place where we describe,

00:20:59.226 --> 00:21:02.186 A:middle
or give you a summary of how
this element's being described.


WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:20:59.226 --> 00:21:02.186 A:middle
or give you a summary of how
this element's being described.

00:21:02.546 --> 00:21:06.606 A:middle
So in this case the eight-dot
button, we'll just say 8.

00:21:07.196 --> 00:21:09.646 A:middle
And to the right there's
the Navigation button

00:21:09.646 --> 00:21:11.846 A:middle
that allows you to
easily navigate

00:21:11.846 --> 00:21:16.346 A:middle
