00:21:48.656 --> 00:21:52.006 A:middle
And so you could simply click
on the Perform button to verify

00:21:52.346 --> 00:21:53.316 A:middle
that this action works.

00:21:56.256 --> 00:21:58.146 A:middle
So that's a highlight
of Inspection.

00:21:58.256 --> 00:22:03.346 A:middle
Let me go ahead and
give you a demo of that.


